Privacy Policy for Trade Lord

Effective Date: 12/19/2025

1. Introduction Trade Lord, developed by Trade Lord Inc, is a mobile application that allows users to participate in cryptocurrency trading tournaments. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and protect the information of our users.

2. Information Collection

Personal Information: We collect personal information such as name, email address, and contact details when you register for an account.
Transactional Data: We store transactional data including trading activity, gains, and losses to manage your account and provide transactional history.
Usage Data: Information on how you use the app, including access times, device information, and app interactions.
3. Use of Information The information we collect is used to:

Provide, maintain, and improve the Trade Lord app.
Communicate with you about tournaments, updates, and promotional offers.
Enhance app security and user experience.
Comply with legal obligations.
4. Data Sharing We do not share your personal information with third parties, except:

To comply with legal requirements such as law enforcement requests.
To protect the rights and safety of others.
With service providers who assist us in app operations under confidentiality agreements.
5. User Rights You have the right to access, correct, or delete your personal data. If you wish to exercise these rights, please contact us at github.com/isidat.

6. Data Security We implement a variety of security measures to ensure the safety of your personal information. However, no method of transmission over the Internet, or method of electronic storage, is 100% secure.

7. Changes to This Privacy Policy We may update our Privacy Policy periodically. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page.

8. Contact Us If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at github.com/isidat.

